org.qdt.quingo.quingo

Interface SwitchStatement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Statement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SwitchStatementImpl

    public interface SwitchStatement
extends Statement
    A representation of the model object 'Switch Statement'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Exp Switch Value
    • Switch Body
    • Default Block
    See Also:
    QuingoPackage.getSwitchStatement()
